            </p>
            
            <div style="display:flex;gap:1.5rem;flex-wrap:wrap;">
                <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:.75rem;">
                    <div style="width:40px;height:40px;border-radius:10px;background:var(--success-container);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;color:var(--success);">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg>
                    </div>
                    <span style="font-size:.9rem;font-weight:800;">100% Fair</span>
                </div>
                <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:.75rem;">
                    <div style="width:40px;height:40px;border-radius:10px;background:var(--tertiary-container);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;color:var(--tertiary);">
                         <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 11c0 3.517-1.009 6.799-2.753 9.571m-3.44-2.04l.054-.09A13.916 13.916 0 008 11a4 4 0 118 0c0 1.017-.07 2.019-.203 3m-2.118 6.844A21.88 21.88 0 0015.171 17m3.839 1.132c.645-2.266.99-4.659.99-7.132A8 8 0 008 4.07M3 15.364c.64-1.319 1-2.8 1-4.364 0-1.457.39-2.823 1.07-4"/></svg>
                    </div>
                    <span style="font-size:.9rem;font-weight:800;">Secure Portal</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
