                <p style="font-size:.82rem;margin:0;line-height:1.7;">Module Leaders define research area tags that categorize proposals. Supervisors select their expertise from this shared taxonomy, enabling accurate matching.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Feature 6: Admin Oversight -->
        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
            <div style="background:var(--surface);border-radius:var(--radius-lg);padding:2rem;box-shadow:var(--shadow-sm);border:1px solid var(--outline-variant);height:100%;transition:transform .2s,box-shadow .2s;" onmouseover="this.style.transform='translateY(-4px)';this.style.boxShadow='var(--shadow-md)'" onmouseout="this.style.transform='';this.style.boxShadow='var(--shadow-sm)'">
                <div style="width:48px;height:48px;border-radius:12px;background:var(--success-container);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;color:var(--success);margin-bottom:1.25rem;">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="22" height="22" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z"/></svg>
                </div>
                <h4 style="font-size:1rem;font-weight:800;margin-bottom:.6rem;">Allocation Oversight Dashboard</h4>
                <p style="font-size:.82rem;margin:0;line-height:1.7;">Administrators get a bird's-eye view of all allocations — including match percentages, conflict resolution tools, search, filter, and the ability to reassign pairings.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>


<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
     SECTION 4: WHO IS IT FOR? (ROLE PANELS)
     ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<div style="padding:3rem 0 5rem;position:relative;z-index:1;">
    <div style="text-align:center;max-width:600px;margin:0 auto 3rem;">
        <div style="font-size:.65rem;font-weight:800;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.12em;color:var(--primary);margin-bottom:.75rem;">Built for Everyone</div>
        <h2 style="font-size:2.2rem;font-weight:900;letter-spacing:-.03em;margin-bottom:1rem;">Tailored for Every Role</h2>
        <p style="font-size:.95rem;color:var(--on-surface-variant);">Whether you're submitting your first proposal or managing hundreds of allocations, the system adapts to your needs.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="row g-4" style="max-width:1100px;margin:0 auto;">
        <!-- Student -->
        <div class="col-lg-6">
            <div style="background:var(--surface);border-radius:var(--radius-lg);padding:2.5rem;box-shadow:var(--shadow-sm);border:1px solid var(--outline-variant);border-top:4px solid var(--primary);height:100%;">
                <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:1rem;margin-bottom:1.5rem;">
                    <div style="width:48px;height:48px;border-radius:12px;background:var(--primary-container);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;color:var(--primary);flex-shrink:0;">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="22" height="22" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 14l9-5-9-5-9 5 9 5z"/><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 14l6.16-3.422a12.083 12.083 0 01.665 6.479A11.952 11.952 0 0012 20.055a11.952 11.952 0 00-6.824-2.998 12.078 12.078 0 01.665-6.479L12 14z"/></svg>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h3 style="font-size:1.2rem;font-weight:900;margin:0;">For Students</h3>
                        <p style="font-size:.78rem;color:var(--text-secondary);margin:0;">Final-year project researchers</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <ul style="list-style:none;padding:0;margin:0;">
                    <li style="display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:.75rem;padding:.6rem 0;border-bottom:1px solid var(--outline-variant);">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="var(--primary)" stroke-width="2.5" style="flex-shrink:0;margin-top:2px;"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                        <span style="font-size:.85rem;color:var(--on-surface);">Submit research proposals with title, abstract, research area, and technical stack</span>
                    </li>
                    <li style="display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:.75rem;padding:.6rem 0;border-bottom:1px solid var(--outline-variant);">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="var(--primary)" stroke-width="2.5" style="flex-shrink:0;margin-top:2px;"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                        <span style="font-size:.85rem;color:var(--on-surface);">Track proposal status in real time — Pending, Under Review, or Matched</span>
                    </li>
                    <li style="display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:.75rem;padding:.6rem 0;border-bottom:1px solid var(--outline-variant);">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="var(--primary)" stroke-width="2.5" style="flex-shrink:0;margin-top:2px;"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                        <span style="font-size:.85rem;color:var(--on-surface);">View your matched supervisor's name and contact details once a match is confirmed</span>
                    </li>
                    <li style="display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:.75rem;padding:.6rem 0;">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="var(--primary)" stroke-width="2.5" style="flex-shrink:0;margin-top:2px;"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                        <span style="font-size:.85rem;color:var(--on-surface);">Your identity stays completely anonymous until a supervisor opts in</span>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Supervisor -->
        <div class="col-lg-6">
            <div style="background:var(--surface);border-radius:var(--radius-lg);padding:2.5rem;box-shadow:var(--shadow-sm);border:1px solid var(--outline-variant);border-top:4px solid var(--tertiary);height:100%;">
                <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:1rem;margin-bottom:1.5rem;">
                    <div style="width:48px;height:48px;border-radius:12px;background:var(--tertiary-container);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;color:var(--tertiary);flex-shrink:0;">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="22" height="22" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 5H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2M9 5a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2M9 5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2m-3 7h3m-3 4h3m-6-4h.01M9 16h.01"/></svg>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h3 style="font-size:1.2rem;font-weight:900;margin:0;">For Supervisors</h3>
                        <p style="font-size:.78rem;color:var(--text-secondary);margin:0;">Academic research mentors</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <ul style="list-style:none;padding:0;margin:0;">
                    <li style="display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:.75rem;padding:.6rem 0;border-bottom:1px solid var(--outline-variant);">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="var(--tertiary)" stroke-width="2.5" style="flex-shrink:0;margin-top:2px;"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                        <span style="font-size:.85rem;color:var(--on-surface);">Declare your research expertise areas to receive relevant proposals</span>
                    </li>
                    <li style="display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:.75rem;padding:.6rem 0;border-bottom:1px solid var(--outline-variant);">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="var(--tertiary)" stroke-width="2.5" style="flex-shrink:0;margin-top:2px;"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                        <span style="font-size:.85rem;color:var(--on-surface);">Browse fully anonymized student proposals — no names, no bias</span>
                    </li>
                    <li style="display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:.75rem;padding:.6rem 0;border-bottom:1px solid var(--outline-variant);">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="var(--tertiary)" stroke-width="2.5" style="flex-shrink:0;margin-top:2px;"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                        <span style="font-size:.85rem;color:var(--on-surface);">Click "Interested" to match — student identity is immediately revealed to you</span>
                    </li>
                    <li style="display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:.75rem;padding:.6rem 0;">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="var(--tertiary)" stroke-width="2.5" style="flex-shrink:0;margin-top:2px;"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                        <span style="font-size:.85rem;color:var(--on-surface);">Manage matched projects and contact students directly from your dashboard</span>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Module Leader / Admin (Full Width) -->
        <div class="col-12">
            <div style="background:linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary) 0%, var(--primary-dim) 100%);border-radius:var(--radius-lg);padding:2.5rem 3rem;box-shadow:var(--shadow-md);display:flex;gap:3rem;align-items:center;flex-wrap:wrap;color:var(--on-primary);">
                <div style="flex:1;min-width:280px;">
                    <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:1rem;margin-bottom:1.25rem;">
                        <div style="width:48px;height:48px;border-radius:12px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.15);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0;">
                            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="22" height="22" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><rect x="3" y="3" width="7" height="7"/><rect x="14" y="3" width="7" height="7"/><rect x="14" y="14" width="7" height="7"/><rect x="3" y="14" width="7" height="7"/></svg>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h3 style="font-size:1.2rem;font-weight:900;margin:0;color:#fff;">For Administrators & Module Leaders</h3>
                            <p style="font-size:.78rem;color:rgba(230,240,242,.7);margin:0;">System management & oversight</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <p style="font-size:.9rem;line-height:1.75;color:rgba(230,240,242,.9);margin:0 0 1.25rem;max-width:520px;">
                        Full visibility over the entire allocation lifecycle. Create research area tags, view match statistics, resolve conflicts, search / filter all proposals, and reassign student–supervisor pairings when needed.
                    </p>
                    @if (!isSignedIn)
                    {
                        <a asp-area="Identity" asp-page="/Account/Login" class="btn" style="background:#fff;color:var(--primary);font-weight:800;padding:.7rem 1.5rem;">
                            Sign In as Admin
                        </a>
                    }
                    else if (User.IsInRole("System Administrator") || User.IsInRole("Module Leader"))
                    {
                        <a asp-controller="Admin" asp-action="Dashboard" class="btn" style="background:#fff;color:var(--primary);font-weight:800;padding:.7rem 1.5rem;">
                            Open Dashboard
                        </a>
                    }
                </div>
                <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:.75rem;min-width:220px;">
                    <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:.75rem;background:rgba(255,255,255,.1);padding:.85rem 1.25rem;border-radius:var(--radius-sm);">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                        <span style="font-size:.82rem;font-weight:600;">Manage Research Areas</span>
                    </div>
                    <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:.75rem;background:rgba(255,255,255,.1);padding:.85rem 1.25rem;border-radius:var(--radius-sm);">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                        <span style="font-size:.82rem;font-weight:600;">View Match Statistics</span>
                    </div>
                    <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:.75rem;background:rgba(255,255,255,.1);padding:.85rem 1.25rem;border-radius:var(--radius-sm);">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                        <span style="font-size:.82rem;font-weight:600;">Reassign Pairings</span>
                    </div>
                    <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:.75rem;background:rgba(255,255,255,.1);padding:.85rem 1.25rem;border-radius:var(--radius-sm);">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                        <span style="font-size:.82rem;font-weight:600;">Search & Filter Allocations</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>


<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
     SECTION 5: CTA BANNER
     ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
@if (!isSignedIn)
{
<div style="padding:0 0 5rem;position:relative;z-index:1;">
    <div style="background:var(--surface);border-radius:var(--radius-xl);padding:4rem 2rem;text-align:center;border:1px solid var(--outline-variant);box-shadow:var(--shadow-md);position:relative;overflow:hidden;">
        <!-- Decorative circles -->
        <div style="position:absolute;top:-60px;right:-60px;width:200px;height:200px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--primary-container);opacity:.5;"></div>
        <div style="position:absolute;bottom:-40px;left:-40px;width:160px;height:160px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--tertiary-container);opacity:.4;"></div>

        <div style="position:relative;z-index:1;">
            <div style="width:56px;height:56px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--primary-container);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;margin:0 auto 1.5rem;color:var(--primary);">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="26" height="26" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M18 9v3m0 0v3m0-3h3m-3 0h-3m-2-5a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0zM3 20a6 6 0 0112 0v1H3v-1z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h2 style="font-size:2rem;font-weight:900;letter-spacing:-.03em;margin-bottom:.75rem;">Ready to Get Started?</h2>
            <p style="font-size:.95rem;color:var(--on-surface-variant);max-width:480px;margin:0 auto 2rem;">
                Create your free account and experience a transparent, bias-free project allocation process designed for academic excellence.
            </p>
            <div style="display:flex;gap:1rem;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;">
                <a asp-area="Identity" asp-page="/Account/Register" class="btn btn-gradient" style="padding:.85rem 2.5rem;font-size:.95rem;">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M18 9v3m0 0v3m0-3h3m-3 0h-3m-2-5a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0zM3 20a6 6 0 0112 0v1H3v-1z"/></svg>
                    Create Free Account
                </a>
                <a asp-area="Identity" asp-page="/Account/Login" class="btn btn-outline" style="padding:.85rem 2rem;font-size:.95rem;">
                    Already a member? Sign In
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
}
